<l>viḷiyumeṉ ṉiṉṉuyir vēṟalla meṉpā</l>
<l> raḷiyiṉmai yāṟṟa niṉaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My precious life is wasting away by thinking too much on the cruelty of him who said we were not different.</l>
